App object and coding style
---------------------------

A Shoes App object is a single window running code at a Shoes URL. When you switch Shoes URLs, a new App object is created. The App itself is a flow. There are three Shoes App object coding styles:

	# sample16.rb
	Shoes.app :width => 150, :height => 40 do
	  para 'Hello world!', :align => 'center'
	end
	  

